#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:1
msgid "回测引擎与性能（设计视角）"
msgstr "Backtesting engine and performance (design perspective)"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:3
msgid ""
"本章从**架构与实现**角度说明 qteasy 回测引擎的向量化与 Numba 使用方式，以及与 "
"VectorBT 等框架的差异，供需要深入理解或做技术选型的读者参考。使用层面的说明见"
"《回测并评价交易策略》中的 [6. 回测引擎与性能](../back_testing/"
"6.%20backtest_engine_and_performance.md)。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter explains, from the perspective of **architecture and "
"implementation**, how qteasy’s backtesting engine uses vectorization and Numba, "
"and how it differs from frameworks such as VectorBT, for readers who need a "
"deeper understanding or are making technical choices. For usage-level "
"explanations, see [6. Backtesting Engine and Performance](../back_testing/"
"6.%20backtest_engine_and_performance.md) in “Backtest and Evaluate Trading "
"Strategies”."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:5
msgid "1. 回测引擎在整体中的位置"
msgstr "1. The role of the backtesting engine in the overall system"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:7
msgid ""
"回测模式（mode=1）的流程在 [回测、实盘与优化](06-backtest-live-optimization.md) "
"中已概括：准备历史数据 → 构建 Backtester → 按 group_timing_table 逐步运行 "
"Operator 生成信号 → 解析信号并模拟成交 → 评价与输出。其中，“解析信号并模拟成交”"
"由 **backtest** 模块中的 Numba 函数完成，实现“时间维顺序、标的维向量化”。"
msgstr ""
"The workflow of backtest mode (mode=1) is summarized in [Backtesting, Live "
"Trading, and Optimization](06-backtest-live-optimization.md): prepare "
"historical data → build the Backtester → run the Operator step by step "
"according to group_timing_table to generate signals → parse signals and "
"simulate fills → evaluate and output. Among these, “parse signals and simulate "
"fills” is handled by the Numba functions in the **backtest** module, achieving "
"“sequential along the time dimension, vectorized along the instrument "
"dimension”."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:9
msgid "2. Numba 使用点与向量化结构"
msgstr "2. Numba usage points and vectorized structures"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:11
msgid "2.1 核心函数"
msgstr "2.1 Core functions"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:13
msgid "在 `qteasy/backtest.py` 中："
msgstr "In `qteasy/backtest.py`:"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:15
msgid ""
"**backtest_step**：`@njit(nogil=True, cache=True)`。单步内根据信号与当前持仓、现"
"金、交割队列，计算买卖量、费用、持仓更新与交割队列更新；对整批标的做数组运算。"
msgstr ""
"**backtest_step**: `@njit(nogil=True, cache=True)`. Within a single step, based "
"on the signals and the current positions, cash, and settlement queue, it "
"computes buy/sell quantities, fees, position updates, and settlement-queue "
"updates; it performs array operations over the entire batch of instruments."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:16
msgid "**calculate_trade_results**：`@njit`，用于交易结果与资金变动计算。"
msgstr ""
"**calculate_trade_results**: `@njit`, used for calculating trade results and "
"cash changes."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:17
msgid ""
"**backtest_batch_steps**：`@njit(nogil=True, cache=True)`。在 Numba 内按 "
"`signal_count`（时间步数）循环，每步调用 `backtest_step`，完成整段回测，实现“时"
"间维顺序、标的维向量化”。"
msgstr ""
"**backtest_batch_steps**: `@njit(nogil=True, cache=True)`. It loops inside "
"Numba by `signal_count` (number of time steps); at each step it calls "
"`backtest_step` to complete the whole backtest segment, achieving “sequential "
"along the time dimension, vectorized along the instrument dimension”."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:18
msgid ""
"**backtest_flash_steps**：`@njit(nogil=True, cache=True)`。与 "
"`backtest_batch_steps` 类似，但不保留中间资金与持仓序列，仅保留最终状态，用于优"
"化阶段多组参数回测时节省内存。"
msgstr ""
"**backtest_flash_steps**: `@njit(nogil=True, cache=True)`. Similar to "
"`backtest_batch_steps`, but it does not retain intermediate cash and position "
"series—only the final state is kept—to save memory during the optimization "
"phase when backtesting multiple parameter sets."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:20
msgid ""
"在 `qteasy/blender.py` 中，信号混合用的部分算子（如 `op_sum`、`op_floor` 等）也"
"使用 `@njit` 加速。"
msgstr ""
"In `qteasy/blender.py`, some operators used for signal blending (such as "
"`op_sum`, `op_floor`, etc.) also use `@njit` for acceleration."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:22
msgid "2.2 时间维顺序与标的维向量化"
msgstr ""
"2.2 Time-Dimension Ordering and Vectorization Along the Instrument Dimension"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:24
msgid ""
"**时间维必须顺序**：因为存在交割队列、T+1、MOQ 等状态，下一笔交易依赖当前持仓与"
"交割状态，无法在时间轴上完全并行或一次性矩阵化。"
msgstr ""
"**The time dimension must be sequential**: because there are states such as the "
"settlement queue, T+1, MOQ, etc., the next trade depends on the current "
"positions and settlement state, so it cannot be fully parallelized along the "
"time axis or matrixized all at once."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:25
msgid ""
"**标的维向量化**：在每一个时间步内，对所有标的的 signal、持仓、买卖量、费用等用 "
"NumPy 数组与 Numba 内联运算，避免 Python 层循环。"
msgstr ""
"**Instrument-dimension vectorization**: within each time step, use NumPy arrays "
"and inlined operations inside Numba for all instruments’ signals, positions, "
"buy/sell quantities, fees, etc., avoiding Python-level loops."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:27
msgid ""
"因此，单次回测可以理解为：**一层 Numba 内的时间步循环 + 每步内的向量化计算**。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, a single backtest can be understood as: **a time-step loop inside "
"one Numba layer + vectorized computation within each step**."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:29
msgid "2.3 优化阶段"
msgstr "2.3 Optimization stage"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:31
msgid ""
"在 `qteasy/optimization.py` 中，多组参数通过多进程（如 `ProcessPoolExecutor`）并"
"行执行回测；每组内部使用 `backtest_flash_steps` 等路径，只保留最终资金/持仓，以"
"降低内存占用并提高吞吐。"
msgstr ""
"In `qteasy/optimization.py`, multiple parameter sets run backtests in parallel "
"via multiprocessing (e.g., `ProcessPoolExecutor`); within each set it uses "
"paths such as `backtest_flash_steps`, keeping only the final cash/positions to "
"reduce memory usage and increase throughput."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:33
msgid "3. 与 VectorBT 的架构差异"
msgstr "3. Architectural differences from VectorBT"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "维度"
msgstr "Dimension"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "qteasy"
msgstr "qteasy"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "VectorBT"
msgstr "VectorBT"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "时间维度"
msgstr "Time dimension"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "顺序步进（for 步），每步内向量化"
msgstr "Sequential stepping (for-loop steps), vectorized within each step"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "全时间轴一次性矩阵运算，无显式时间循环"
msgstr ""
"One-shot matrix operations over the full timeline, with no explicit time loop"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "标的维度"
msgstr "Asset dimension"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "每步对全部标的做数组运算（1D 数组）"
msgstr "At each step, perform array operations on all assets (1D arrays)"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "标的与时间一起参与广播，多策略/多参数可一并广播"
msgstr ""
"The instrument and time participate in broadcasting together; multiple "
"strategies/multiple parameter sets can be broadcast in one go."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "核心加速"
msgstr "Core acceleration"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid ""
"backtest_step、backtest_batch_steps、backtest_flash_steps 等为 @njit；信号解析、"
"交割队列等也用 Numba"
msgstr ""
"`backtest_step`, `backtest_batch_steps`, `backtest_flash_steps`, etc. are "
"`@njit`; signal parsing, the settlement/delivery queue, etc. also use Numba."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "NumPy + Numba，策略表达为纯数组运算"
msgstr "NumPy + Numba, with strategies expressed as pure array operations"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "状态与约束"
msgstr "States and constraints"

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "显式维护现金、持仓、交割队列（T+1 等），状态依赖下一笔，故时间维必须顺序"
msgstr ""
"Explicitly maintains cash, positions, and a settlement/delivery queue (T+1, "
"etc.); the state depends on the next trade, so the time dimension must be "
"sequential."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md
msgid "多为简化资金曲线，不强调 T+1/交割/MOQ，易做全矩阵"
msgstr ""
"Mostly a simplified equity curve, without emphasizing T+1/settlement/MOQ, "
"making it easy to build a full matrix."

#: ../../source/design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md:42
msgid ""
"**结论**：qteasy 并非“缺乏向量化/Numba”，而是在保证**状态正确性**（T+1、交割、"
"MOQ、多策略合并等）的前提下，选择了“时间顺序 + 标的维向量化 + Numba 单步”的折"
"中；与 VectorBT 的“全矩阵广播”各有适用场景（qteasy 偏规则严谨与实盘一致，"
"VectorBT 偏海量参数快速筛选）。"
msgstr ""
"**Conclusion**: qteasy is not “lacking vectorization/Numba”; rather, on the "
"premise of ensuring **state correctness** (T+1, settlement, MOQ, multi-strategy "
"merging, etc.), it chose a compromise of “time-ordered + instrument-dimension "
"vectorization + Numba per-step”; it and VectorBT’s “full-matrix broadcasting” "
"each have their own applicable scenarios (qteasy leans toward rigorous rules "
"and consistency with live trading, while VectorBT leans toward rapid screening "
"over massive parameter grids)."

